         * System call from user mode.
         * LoongArch convention: a7 = syscall number, a0-a5 = arguments.
         * Register layout in trap_frame (regs[N] = $rN):
         *   regs[4]  = $r4  = a0
         *   regs[5]  = $r5  = a1
         *   regs[6]  = $r6  = a2
         *   regs[11] = $r11 = a7
